node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Gaten Matarazzo on July 26, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, beard, child, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Sending love and prayers to the Omstead family. Tragically last week Albert passed in an accident working on his home. He worked on our set and helped to create the wonderful show that has given so much comfort and warmth to so many. Only wish I had the pleasure of knowing him. Just through the stories I was lucky to hear from his friends and family, it’s clear he was a power house of a person. A funny, caring, hard working, firecracker of a man. Sending love to his wife Que and to his five kids. He is a prime example of the incredible, And massive community it takes to make a show like this. What a smile. If you feel obliged at all you can help the family by going to https://gofund.me/629f2394.❤️ rest well.

node.text: Round two! Fully vaccinated! If you’re in the Atlantic City NJ area please go to the Atlantic City Convention Center to get your vaccinations. They’re accepting walk in’s!!!! It’s so easy and so quick. Let’s all do our part to fight back against COVID-19. Wear a mask. Get vaccinated. Socially distance. Wash your hands. If not out of concern for yourself, than out of concern for those around you. You can make a serious difference. #acmegasite
